vernac_cmds: From mathcomp Require Import ssreflect ssrfun ssrbool ssrnat seq eqtype.
From LemmaOverloading Require Import prelude prefix heaps terms.
Structure abs_pts x pts_A (pts_v : pts_A) pts_r := AbsPts { pts_h :> pack_heap; _ : pack_h pts_h = x :-> pts_v :+ pts_r }.
Definition pts_inv x A (v :A) r (f : abs_pts x v r) := match f return (pack_h f = x:->v:+r) with (AbsPts p i) => i end.
Program Canonical pts_found A x (v : A) := AbsPts x v empty (pack_found (x :-> v)) _.
by move=>A x v; rewrite unh0.
Program Canonical pts_left x A (v:A) r (a : abs_pts x v r) rh := AbsPts x v (r :+ rh) (pack_left (a :+ rh)) _.
Program Canonical pts_right x A (v:A) r (a : abs_pts x v r) lh := AbsPts x v (lh :+ r) (pack_right (lh :+ a)) _.
Structure abs_heap h1 r := AbsHeap { heap_h :> pack_heap; _ : pack_h heap_h = h1 :+ r }.
Definition heap_inv h r (f : abs_heap h r) := match f return pack_h f = h :+ r with AbsHeap h' i => i end.
Program Canonical heap_found h := AbsHeap h empty (pack_found h) _.
Program Canonical heap_left h r (a : abs_heap h r) rh := AbsHeap h (r :+ rh) (pack_left (a :+ rh)) _.
Program Canonical heap_right h r (a : abs_heap h r) lh := AbsHeap h (lh :+ r) (pack_right (lh :+ a)) _.
Structure heapeq lh rh r (D : def rh) (I : lh :+ r = rh) := HeapEq { dummy : trigger; prop : Prop; proof : prop }.
Program Canonical ins1 := @HeapEq empty empty empty def0 _ pack00 _ I.
Program Canonical ins2 h2 (d : def h2) (i : empty :+ empty = h2) := @HeapEq empty h2 empty d i (pack01 tt) (h2 = empty) _.
Program Canonical ins3 h2 r (d : def h2) (i : empty :+ r = h2) := @HeapEq empty h2 r d i (pack02 tt) (h2 = r) _.

Program Canonical ins4 x A (v : A) r A' (v':A') r' (pf : abs_pts x v' r') (d : def (pts_h pf)) (i : x:->v :+ r = (pts_h pf)) (rec : @heapeq empty r' r _ _) := @HeapEq (x:->v) (pts_h pf) r d i (pack03 (dummy rec)) (dyn v = dyn v' /\ prop rec) _.
move=>x A v r A' v' r' [h2 /= ->] D H.
move=>x A v r A' v' r' [h2 /= ->] D H.
move=>x A v r A' v' r' [h2 /= I] D H rec.
Program Canonical ins5 x A (v : A) h2 r (d : def h2) (i : x:->v :+ r = h2) (rec : @heapeq empty h2 (x:->v :+ r) d _) := @HeapEq (x:->v) h2 r d i (pack04 (dummy rec)) _ (proof rec).

Program Canonical ins6 x A (v : A) h1 r A' (v' : A') r' (pf : abs_pts x v' r') (d : def (pts_h pf)) (i : (x:->v :+ h1) :+ r = (pts_h pf)) (rec : @heapeq h1 r' r _ _) := @HeapEq (x:->v:+h1) (pts_h pf) r d i (pack05 (dummy rec)) (dyn v = dyn v' /\ prop rec) _.
move=>x A v h1 r A' v' r' [h2 /= ->] D H.
move=>x A v h1 r A' v' r' [h2 /= ->] D H.
move=>x A v h1 r A' v' r' [h2 /= I] D H rec.
Program Canonical ins7 x A (v : A) h1 h2 r (d : def h2) (i : (x:->v :+ h1) :+ r = h2) (rec : @heapeq h1 h2 (x:->v:+r) d _) := @HeapEq (x:->v:+h1) h2 r d i (pack06 (dummy rec)) _ (proof rec).
move=>x A v h1 h2 r D H.

Program Canonical ins8 h1 h2 r r' (pf : abs_heap h1 r') (d : def (heap_h pf)) (i : (h1 :+ h2) :+ r = heap_h pf) (rec : @heapeq h2 r' r _ _) := @HeapEq (h1 :+ h2) (heap_h pf) r d i (pack07 (dummy rec)) _ (proof rec).
move=>h1 h2 r r' [hr /= ->] D H.
move=>h1 h2 r r' [hr /= I] D H.
Program Canonical ins9 h1 h2 r hr (d : def hr) (i : (h1 :+ h2) :+ r = hr) (rec : @heapeq h2 hr (h1 :+ r) d _) := @HeapEq (h1 :+ h2) hr r d i (pack08 (dummy rec)) _ (proof rec).

Program Canonical ins10 h1 r r' (pf : abs_heap h1 r') (d : def (heap_h pf)) (i : h1 :+ r = heap_h pf) (rec : @heapeq empty r' r _ _) := @HeapEq h1 (heap_h pf) r d i (pack09 (dummy rec)) _ (proof rec).
move=>h1 r r' [hr /= I] D H.
by rewrite un0h; apply (eqUh D H).
Canonical insLast h1 h2 r (d : def h2) (i : h1 :+r = h2) := @HeapEq h1 h2 r d i (pack10 tt) (h1 :+ r = h2) i.
Lemma cancel1 : forall h1 h2 : heap, def h1 -> h1 = h2 -> def h2.
Lemma cancel2 : forall h1 h2 : heap, h1 = h2 -> h1 :+ empty = h2.
Lemma cancel (h1 h2 : heap) (D : def h1) (H : h1 = h2) (c : @heapeq h1 h2 empty (cancel1 D H) (cancel2 H)) : tt = dummy c -> prop c.
Time set H' := cancel D H (erefl _).

command: by move=>A x v; rewrite unh0.
move=>x A v r A' v' r' [h2 /= ->] D H.
move=>x A v r A' v' r' [h2 /= ->] D H.
move=>x A v r A' v' r' [h2 /= I] D H rec.
move=>x A v h1 r A' v' r' [h2 /= ->] D H.
move=>x A v h1 r A' v' r' [h2 /= ->] D H.
move=>x A v h1 r A' v' r' [h2 /= I] D H rec.
move=>x A v h1 h2 r D H.
move=>h1 h2 r r' [hr /= ->] D H.
move=>h1 h2 r r' [hr /= I] D H.
move=>h1 r r' [hr /= I] D H.
by rewrite un0h; apply (eqUh D H).
Time set H' := cancel D H (erefl _).
